item.title: A introduction to SEO
item.description: In this topic you can find all the information you need about SEO (Search Engine Optimalization) What is SEO # SEO or Search Engine Optimalization is optimizing your live projects so that it can be found by search engines. SEO consists of a list of rules to live by, by following these rules you are optimizing your site to be found first by a search engine. Shortly: Follow the rules and get a higher rank in search engines.
